  <brief_title>Moxifloxacin i.v. in the Treatment of Complicated Intra-Abdominal Infection (cIAI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Effectiveness and Safety Study of Moxifloxacin i.v. in the Treatment of Complicated Intra-Abdominal Infection (cIAI)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
