  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a local, prospective, open-label, company-sponsored, non interventional,
      multi-center study. Patients documented must suffer from a cIAI and take at least one dose of
      Moxifloxacin infusion.The primary objective is to define the types of cIAI infections that
      require Moxifloxacin i.v. therapy in China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
